Description:
You reach a hall full of undead and at the end of which you see the obelisk of Ulminin.

You notice that in the middle of the hall there is an ancient sarcophagus and around it there is a kind of lich that seems to have been resurrected with the corrupted energy from the activation of the obelisk.

No doubt the lich is the reason why all the chambers are infested with undead and there is no way to reach the obelisk without defeating it.
DescriptionAction: How do you want to approach combat?
